<SecondaryPreamble>
<EnactingText>
<Para>
<Text>Mae Gweinidogion Cymru, drwy arfer y pwerau a roddwyd i’r Ysgrifennydd Gwladol gan adrannau 89B(1), 89C(2) a 92 o Ddeddf Safonau a Fframwaith Ysgolion 1998<FootnoteRef Ref="f00001"/>, ac a freiniwyd bellach ynddynt hwy<FootnoteRef Ref="f00002"/>, yn gwneud y Rheoliadau a ganlyn.</Text>
</Para>
</EnactingText>
</SecondaryPreamble>
</SecondaryPrelims></Secondary><Footnotes><Footnote id="f00001">
<FootnoteText>
<Para>
<Text><Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/1998/31/welsh" id="c00004" Year="1998" Number="31" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">1998 p. 31</Citation>; gweler adran 90ZA am y diffiniadau o “prescribed” a “regulations”. Mewnosodwyd adran 89B gan Ddeddf Addysg <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2002/32/welsh" id="c00005" Year="2002" Number="32" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">2002 (p. 32)</Citation>, adran 48 ac fe’i diwygiwyd gan Ddeddf Addysg a Sgiliau <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2008/25/welsh" id="c00006" Year="2008" Number="25" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">2008 (p. 25)</Citation>, Atodlen 1, paragraffau 53, 59(1) a (2), ac <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2010/1158/welsh" id="c00007" Year="2010" Number="1158" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument">O.S. 2010/1158</Citation>; mae diwygiadau eraill ond nid yw’r un ohonynt yn berthnasol i’r Rheoliadau hyn. Mewnosodwyd adran 89C gan Ddeddf Addysg <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2002/32/welsh" id="c00008" Year="2002" Number="32" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">2002 (p. 32)</Citation>, adran 48 ac fe’i diwygiwyd gan Ddeddf Addysg a Sgiliau <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2008/25/welsh" id="c00009" Year="2008" Number="25" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">2008 (p. 25)</Citation>, Atodlen 1, paragraffau 53, 60(1), (2) a (3), Deddf Safonau a Threfniadaeth Ysgolion (Cymru) <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/anaw/2013/1/welsh" id="c00010" Year="2013" Number="1" Class="WelshNationalAssemblyAct">2013 (dccc 1)</Citation>, Atodlen 5, paragraff 4(1) a (5) ac <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2010/1158/welsh" id="c00011" Year="2010" Number="1158" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument">O.S. 2010/1158</Citation>; mae diwygiadau eraill ond nid yw’r un ohonynt yn berthnasol i’r Rheoliadau hyn. Amnewidiwyd adran 92 gan Ddeddf Addysg <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2002/32/welsh" id="c00012" Year="2002" Number="32" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">2002 (p. 32)</Citation>, Atodlen 4, paragraff 7 ac fe’i diwygiwyd gan <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2010/1158/welsh" id="c00013" Year="2010" Number="1158" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument">O.S. 2010/1158</Citation>.</Text>
</Para>
</FootnoteText>
</Footnote><Footnote id="f00002">
<FootnoteText>
<Para>
<Text>Trosglwyddwyd swyddogaethau’r Ysgrifennydd Gwladol o dan yr adrannau hyn o Ddeddf Safonau a Fframwaith Ysgolion <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/1998/31/welsh" id="c00014" Year="1998" Number="31" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">1998 (p. 31)</Citation> i Gynulliad Cenedlaethol Cymru gan Orchymyn Cynulliad Cenedlaethol Cymru (Trosglwyddo Swyddogaethau) 1999 (<Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/1999/672/welsh" id="c00015" Year="1999" Number="672" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument">O.S. 1999/672</Citation>) ac yna i Weinidogion Cymru gan Ddeddf Llywodraeth Cymru <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2006/32/welsh" id="c00016" Year="2006" Number="32" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct">2006 (p. 32)</Citation>, Atodlen 11, paragraff 30.</Text>
</Para>
</FootnoteText>
</Footnote></Footnotes></Legislation>
